title: Enhancement: Improve README for clarity
body:
The README file needs updates to improve clarity on project setup and usage. This issue proposes the following changes:

1. Add a detailed setup guide.
2. Include examples for common use cases.
3. Reformat sections to improve readability.

These changes aim to make the README more helpful to new contributors and users.

title: Added a line to README
body:
**Title:**
`[Feature/Fix] - Brief Description of Change`

**Description:**
- What changes were made: _Provide a short summary of the changes._
- Why these changes are necessary: _Explain the problem you're solving or the feature you're adding._
- How does this contribute to the project: _Highlight the benefit of your contribution._

**Checklist:**
- [ ] I have read the project’s contributing guidelines.
- [ ] I have run any necessary tests, and they pass.
- [ ] I have added or updated documentation (if applicable).

**Additional Information (Optional):**
- _Mention any issues or discussions related to this PR._
- _Provide any notes or screenshots that help explain your changes._

**Thank You:**
_Thank you for reviewing my contribution! Please let me know if there are any suggestions or changes needed._
